dc_title_s: Map of Minneapolis, Hennepin Co., Minn., 1897. Plate no. 55, Water mains
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:24,000]. 2,000 ft. to 1 in. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Shows existing and proposed water mains, street car lines and railroads, and parks. On verso: "Plate Number 55. Water Mains."|72 x 47 centimeters|1:24,000|Minneapolis and St. Paul Maps and Atlases
